# Firebase admin auth uses firebase-applet-config.json for public config.
# Create Firebase Auth users manually, then add appAdministrators/{uid}
# in Firestore to unlock /admin real mode.
# Firebase is the primary pilot persistence path for actor applications.
# Supabase remains documented as fallback only.

# Supabase client persistence fallback for actor applications
# Create these tables first: doctor_applications, dispensary_applications.
